        <title>Configuring effects</title>
        <p>To configure an effect, simply select it in the <guiseq><gui>middle pane</gui><gui>Clip configuration</gui> <gui>Effects</gui></guiseq>. Variables that can be adjusted will appear in the lower part of the <gui>Clip configuration</gui> tab. Each variable can be put back to it's original value by clicking the corresponding <gui>Reset to default value</gui> button.</p>
